manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: It would take a lot of time to acquire the 135 ingredients individually to equal what is in Passion 4 Life. Also, if you tried to eat the daily amount of food required to equal what is in our delicious product, it would not only be physically impossible. Even if you think you eat well, the quality of today's soil with its pesticides, herbicides and chemicals greatly devalues the nutrition of the food we eat. Therefore, even the AMA now recommends that everyone takes supplements. Passion 4 Life takes the guesswork out of taking vitamins. No need to walk the aisles of the food store totally baffled what to take and how much. Plus, no need to break the bank to help improve your well-being. We've done the work for you. Additionally, no more hard-to-swallow pills to choke down, many of which only absorb up to 10-20% with the rest being flushed down the toilet literally while Passion 4 Life absorbs up to 98% directly into your bloodstream within 3 minutes of ingestion. · Backed by 15 years of research · Great tasting, Convenient · Perfect for all ages: 1 - 101 · Celiac friendly, Bariatric friendly · "Vitamin with a Mission" - do something good for yourself & a portion of your purchase goes to help U.S. children in need through our 501 (c)(3) charity Passion 4 K.I.D.S. · Family-owned with quality, integrity and outstanding love for our clients are our highest priorities CONTAINS NO: · Gluten, GMOs, Added Sugar · Artificial Flavors, Artificial Colors, Artificial Sweeteners · Dairy, Wheat, Soy · Caffeine _______ CONTAINS: · 135 High-Grade Natural Whole Food-Based Ingredients · All Essential Vitamins, 72 Trace Minerals · Powerful Antioxidants, Critically Important Amino Acids Health Category products such as health drinks, organic supplements and other related products that do not carry any certified disclaimers must have an FDA disclaimer present. (FDA Disclaimer: These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease).

Why Passion 4 Life Was Created I was born in Amsterdam during the beginning of WWII in 1941. At 2, my family was taken, and I ended up in a state-run orphanage. I finally ran away. I lived on the streets of Amsterdam as a 10- year-old for 4 years trying to survive. In December '64 I came to America on a green card. I started taking handfuls of hard-to-swallow vitamin pills to overcome my wellness challenges from malnutrition. I learned that due to poor absorption the vitamin pills didn’t work for me. I studied nutrition for 15 years and created this amazing tasting liquid product to improve my own body. It worked for me so I decided to share it with the world. It's been my mission to turn my tragic beginning into a story of reinvention and hope by combining the 2 things I lacked in life – good nutrition & someone to care. A portion of the vitamin profits help fund our children’s charity. Charles Founder & Creator
